data.description:
One owner, 4BR, 3BA, single story, home in Ashbrooke subdivision will check all your boxes.  Open plan, with new wood flooring in living areas. Separate Dining area. Family Room with gas log fireplace and built-ins. Kitchen - granite counters, decorative backsplash, and an eat-in bar. New dish washer, gas cooktop, and the Refrigerator remains! Off the kitchen is the Laundry room with cabinets for storage - Washer & Dryer remain. The Primary Bedroom/Bath have double vanities with plenty of storage, whirlpool tub, and separate Shower. Large closet with built-ins. 3 additional Bedrooms. Off the family room is the screened porch overlooking the large, flat Fenced backyard. Gutters. 2 car garage with additional storage room. Crown Molding in all rooms. Irrigation in front and back.
Ashbrooke amenities -2 pools, splash pad, clubhouse, playground, greenspace, sidewalks, and a fishing lake.
All located within Germantown school district. Ashbrooke is an AT&T & Cspire Fiber community.
Conveniently located to schools, interstates, shopping and restaurants.
